{
  "stem": "4830.3",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And I told him that I and going with him, because I always felt that I could cope with these things.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "I had an extreme optimism that I will survive.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "As I told you, we were four boys and four girls in a group of people, and I bet with all the boys that I will survive.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "I believe it was $50 that I bet.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And-- and I did survive, but I had nobody to collect from because they all died.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And at any rate, I told that if my brother is going, I will be going with him.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "So we went to a football stadium where I found that they took my brother because it was an over zealous group who attacked our house, and they shouldn't have been taken.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And they said that anybody who is under 16 can go home.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "So my brother could go home, but I was over 16, and I could not.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "And I very much disliked this idea.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I had to act very quickly as I had to do it several times in the remaining few months-- that I told my brother that he should give me-- we had two certificates-- documents with us.",
      "word_count": 37
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "One of them was a personal document.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "The other one was a paramilitary document for everybody.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I asked for his paramilitary document, which showed that I am 14, and my name is Ervin Kohn.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And I asked him to-- we were 18 people lining up.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I asked him to go out first and run in case if they discover me, that I am with the same name.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But they didn't.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I got out with his papers and he was sitting there waiting for me.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So we just walked home.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
